{
  "stem": "24231.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was going to United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was saying, well, I can't take it to United States, because it's written in Czech.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now it has to be translated if anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it can serve better here in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I brought it to-- to-- to this Jewish orphanage in Prague.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of my friends lived there, some of the kids who who returned from different camps, kids I I used to know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a lady who used to have her son on our-- on our-- in our home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lowe ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I gave it to-- to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, look, you know, here is a magazine, which we were issuing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was-- she was aware of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because she used to come in and sometimes clean out in her house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was helping out with cleaning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I gave it to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she never remembered who gave it to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, one day there was a lady who took interest in this magazine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I got a letter that they would like to find out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's the only things that could have happened is how the magazine survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I would-- she would like to find out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I wrote her how the magazine survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I guess in the magazine, when they-- when they issued some of the pages of the magazine in Czech, she put the letter which I wrote to her.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and also, lately it was translated into English through big effort of this fellow, George Brady, who really deserves credit for bringing it-- having it translated into English and bringing it here.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and that's how the magazine is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The magazine, I I don't know exactly how it got-- got there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
